Kendrion Group Services


























Kendrion Linnig Drive Tech. (Nanjing) Co. Ltd.Kendrion Linnig Drive Techn. (Nanjing) Co. Ltd. also belongs to Kendrion's Commercial Vehicle Systems business unit. The Company was established in 2006. It provides innovative electromagnetic solutions for the Chinese market leaders in the bus sector, as well as in the trucking, off-highway and gen-set area.Product PortfolioOur manufacturing location in China primarily focuses on the production of clutch systems for commercial vehicles, such as electromagnetic clutches with angle gearbox, 2 and 3-speed fan clutches as well as various compressor clutches.







