Kendrion Group Services













Kendrion's core competencies
High-quality electromagnetic systems and components






Kendrion develops, manufactures and markets worldwide high-quality electromagnetic systems and components for industrial and automotive applications. Our global footprint extends from Europe and the US to Mexico, India and China.











Kendrion Kuhnke Automation in Medical and Analysis Technology
Solutions for Patient Health







For applications in medical and analysis technology, Kendrion Kuhnke Automation develops ready-to-use components and highly integrated assemblies consisting of solenoids, sensors and control electronics. They serve to reduce the number of interfaces, while increasing functional safety.


